  <title>Gio.TlsConnection.peer_certificate_errors</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
TlsConnection.peer_certificate_errors: <link xref="Gio.TlsCertificateFlags">Gio.TlsCertificateFlags</link> (Read)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>The errors noticed-and-ignored while verifying
<link xref="Gio.TlsConnection-peer-certificate"/>. Normally this should be 0, but
it may not be if <link xref="Gio.TlsClientConnection-validation-flags"/> is not
<link xref="Gio.TlsCertificateFlags"/>.validate_all, or if
<link xref="Gio.TlsConnection-accept-certificate"/> overrode the default
behavior.</p>
